<plot>Imagine waking up in a room that is not yours, or is it but you can't remember? Imagine not knowing your name why you are trapped in this room. All that you find is a telephone and a TV. You are not alone in the room. H-49 is not aware he is participating in a reality TV show. The participants have a microchip embedded into their brains that broadcasts what they see in the room. His microchip malfunctions and he starts loosing his mind as he struggles to break free from the room.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?226204</url></doc>
